narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 111 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 111 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Great seminar about a very interesting and politically relevant topic; explores many of the most salient debates in journalism today; well designed and executed by Professor Slap, who is also able to provide intimate commentary about some of the topics we cover given his background in the news industry; facilitates engaging class conversation; great reading selection; would definitely recommend to other students
yea overall was good and the books were interesting.
